prompts.frontCover:
Flat 2D watercolor painting of a humorous and lighthearted birthday scene. In the foreground, there is an illustrated cartoon couple, highly resembling the people in the reference photo. On the left is Lao Lao, an East Asian woman with long, straight dark hair, smiling warmly and wearing thin, round, gold-rimmed glasses and a pale yellow halter top with a pink floral pattern. On the right is Jordan, a man with light-to-medium skin, a big joyful smile, and short, spiky dark hair. He is wearing a simple white t-shirt. The couple is drawn as if they are trying to fit into an old-fashioned, small, and slightly rickety wooden roller coaster car. Lao Lao is crammed in comically but looking amused, while Jordan is squeezed in beside her, looking slightly squashed but laughing. The background is a soft, light-blue sky with whimsical, fluffy white clouds, all rendered in a soft, flowing watercolor style with visible paper texture, artistic brush strokes, and organic paint bleeds.

In the center of the card, in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script, is the text: "Happy Birthday, Lao Lao! Life is a wild ride with you."

- Reference photos provided for character creation
- Characters should only appear on the front cover
- Transform real people into artistic cartoon/illustrated versions matching the style
- Maintain recognizable features while adapting to the artistic style
